parameters: Umi "Thank Mia. I've been watching you all this time."

Umi "What happened? It's the first time Mia's been friendly with a
stranger."

Kru "Ah. I came across this kid being attacked by a monster. I defeated the
monster, but then... I fell off a cliff..."
Kru "Hahaha, that tickles. I'm fine. Are you hurt at all?"
Umi "I see... Thank you. Mia is safe because of you... Eat this."
Kru "Thank you. You took care of me, didn't you?"
Umi "Mia was always there. Umi only occasionally."
Umi "Umi is Umi. Cat is Mia."
Kru "I see. I'm Kru. Thank you for saving me, Umi."
Kru "Don't say you didn't do anything... I'm really grateful..."
Kru "Yeah! Man, I thought I was dead when I fell."
Kru "Yeah, that's true. I'm thankful for the coincidence!"
Villager "Umi. The chieftain is calling for you."
Umi "I'm going to the chieftain's place. Can you stand?"
Umi: "This has become such a hassle."
Kru: "Is that what's-it-called cave really that dangerous?"
Umi: "The cave is far. Umi hates getting tired."
Kru: "Eh? You're not going? The chieftain will be angry, you know."
Umi: "Let the chieftain be angry. Umi hates the chieftain."

Kru: "No way, that's harsh. The chieftain doesn't seem like such a bad
person."

Umi: "The chieftain is a good person. Gives delicious things. Umi liked the
chieftain until yesterday. Today, Umi hates."
Kru: "Miss Umi, you're quite moody, aren't you?"

Umi: "Mia... don't be so mad... I apologize for speaking ill of the
chieftain."
Umi: "Sigh, understood. I'll go to the cave."
Kru: "Eh! Mia said that? And you listen to Mia..."

Umi: "Mia is Umi's family. Umi listens to what Mia says. Mia listens to
what Umi says."

Kru: "I don't quite understand, but thank you. I owe you for your
hospitality."
Umi: "Sigh. The southern exit of the village. From there, head west."
